BGM絕大多是電影[[enwiki:Intersection_(1994_film)]]的主题曲《Hear Me Cry》的純音樂版<ref>http://music.163.com/#/song/5197149/</ref><!--http://www.bilibili.com/video/av142091/index_1.html-->
